+// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
+/*
+ * TM16xx and compatible LED display/keypad controller driver
+ * Supports TM16xx, FD6xx, PT6964, HBS658, AIP16xx and related chips.
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2025 Jean-François Lessard
